{"lemma":"مُلْسُ","slug":"مُلْسُ","root":"م.ل.س","root_slug":"م-ل-س","root_link":"/words/roots/م-ل-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n38914","n38918","n38919"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%92%D8%B3%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become smooth, to glide, slip away"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n38914","headword_ar":"مَلُسَ","root":"mls","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, A, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malisa","text_ar":"مَلِسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) or the second form is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malasa","text_ar":"مَلَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) [but the last of the inf. ns. here following seems to indicate that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malisa","text_ar":"مَلِسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is correct;] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaAsapN","text_ar":"مَلَاسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muluwsapN","text_ar":"مُلُوسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) [accord. to rule, both of the first,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malasN","text_ar":"مَلَسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) [accord. to rule, of the second;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, smooth, sleek,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"free from asperities;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the inf. n. being the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu$uwnapN","text_ar":"خُشُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it had in it nothing upon which to lay hold; it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, smooth to the feel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AmlAs~","text_ar":"املاسّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (S, M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_imoliysaAsN","text_ar":"اـِمْلِيسَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Amls~","text_ar":"املسّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (so in a copy of the A) and [in like manner] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tml~s","text_ar":"تملّس","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_im~alasa","text_ar":"اـِمَّلَسَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inofaEala","text_ar":"اـِنْفَعَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n","text_ar":"ن"},{"kind":"text","text":"being incorporated into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":", both signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered, smooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (S.) See also 4.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malasa","text_ar":"مَلَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malosN","text_ar":"مَلْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went away quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swiftly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malasati Aln~aAqapu","text_ar":"مَلَسَتِ النَّاقَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_ibilu","text_ar":"الاـِبِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) aor. and inf. n. as before, (M,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the she-camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swiftly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malosN","text_ar":"مَلْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going easily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gently:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also, contr., the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going vehemently:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gentle mode of going"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active, and quick."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siro valaAvFA","text_ar":"سِرْ ثَلَاثًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malosFA","text_ar":"مَلْسًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAva layaAlK *awaAti malosK","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَ لَيَالٍ ذَوَاتِ مَلْسٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvFA sayorFA malosFA","text_ar":"ثَلَاثًا سَيْرًا مَلْسًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Journey thou three nights of quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of easy, journeying;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an easy, journeying;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mlsA","text_ar":"ملسا"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies a certain mode of going or journeying; and is in the accus. case as an inf. n. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malasa","text_ar":"مَلَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above, also signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went back,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inoxanasa","text_ar":"اـِنْخَنَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_im~alasa","text_ar":"اـِمَّلَسَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malasa AlZ~alaAmu","text_ar":"مَلَسَ الظَّلَامُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (TK,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malosN","text_ar":"مَلْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malasN","text_ar":"مَلَسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The darkness became confused;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amolasa","text_ar":"اَمْلَسَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_imolaAsN","text_ar":"اـِمْلَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became in the state after that which is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malavN","text_ar":"مَلَثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malovN","text_ar":"مَلْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malosN","text_ar":"مَلْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below."}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Msb","K","TA","IAar","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n38918","headword_ar":"مَلْسٌ","root":"mls","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amolasu","text_ar":"اَمْلَسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malosN","text_ar":"مَلْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malasN","text_ar":"مَلَسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confusedness"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the darkness: (S, M, A, K:) or it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malav","text_ar":"مَلَث"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malov","text_ar":"مَلْث"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mlv","text_ar":"ملث"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the first, or commencement, of the blackness of the west; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mls","text_ar":"ملس"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the blackness has become intense, so that the time of the last"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei$aA='","text_ar":"عِشَا=ء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comes;"},{"kind":"text","text":"then the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mls","text_ar":"ملس"},{"kind":"text","text":"becomes confounded with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mlv","text_ar":"ملث"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the one is not distinguished from the other. (IAar.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~alaAmi","text_ar":"الظَّلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu malasa","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ مَلَسَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malosa AlZlAm","text_ar":"مَلْسَ الظلام"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him when the darkness had become confused;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the night had become confused with the earth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) The word is used adverbially and otherwise. (M.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malasa AlZ~alaAmu","text_ar":"مَلَسَ الظَّلَامُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["A","K","S","M","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n38919","headword_ar":"مَلَسٌ","root":"mls","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_imoliysN","text_ar":"اـِمْلِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places:       -A2-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malosN","text_ar":"مَلْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", throughout."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}